org.xlattice.corexml.om

Class NodeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.corexml.om.NodeList

  • public class NodeList
extends java.lang.Object
    A container for Nodes. Each Holder (Document or Element) has a NodeList, but the reverse is not necessarily true.

    XXX NEED TO SIMPLIFY THE HANDLING OF THE ELEMENT NODE IN A XXX DOCUMENT
